# Google Sheets XLSX URL
# This is the XLSX export URL for the r/progmetal releases spreadsheet
# XLSX format preserves hyperlinks, unlike CSV export
# NOTE: Do NOT include &gid parameter - the system now processes ALL prog-metal tabs automatically
